#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.knavalbattle.appdata.xml:9
msgid "Naval Battle"
msgstr "Pomorska bitka"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.knavalbattle.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Battle Ship Game"
msgstr "Igra potapanja brodova"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.knavalbattle.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"Naval Battle is a ship sinking game. Ships are placed on a board which "
"represents the sea. Players try to hit each others ships in turns without "
"knowing where they are placed. The first player to destroy all ships wins "
"the game."
msgstr ""
"Pomorska bitka je igra potapanja brodova. Brodovi se smeštaju na tablu koja "
"predstavlja more. Igrači pokušavaju jedan drugom da pogode brodove, za koje "
"ne znaju gde su postavljeni. Prvi igrač koji uništi sve brodove dobija "
"partiju."
